e:T73f,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Semrush better than Ubersuggest?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Semrush scores 9.0 overall while Ubersuggest scores 6.0. Semrush is best for SEO professionals and digital agencies, while Ubersuggest excels for beginners and solopreneurs."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Semrush or Ubersuggest?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Semrush starts at $139.95/mo and Ubersuggest starts at $29/mo.  Ubersuggest offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Semrush to Ubersuggest?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Semrush and Ubersuggest support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Semrush vs Ubersuggest?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Semrush holds an overall rating of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Ubersuggest has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Semrush for most comprehensive seo toolkit available and Ubersuggest for very affordable with lifetime plan option."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Semrush or Ubersuggest?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Semrush for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Ubersuggest remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize very affordable with lifetime plan option. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-head