14:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Semrush and Ubersuggest share a solid foundation of core features including Keyword Research, Rank Tracking, Site Audit, Backlink Analysis. Where Semrush pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Semrush holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Ubersuggest scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
15:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Ubersuggest comes in at a lower starting price of $29/mo, while Semrush begins at $139.95/mo. Ubersuggest stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Semrush requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
