18:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Semrush is best suited for SEO professionals, digital agencies, marketing teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Ubersuggest, meanwhile, shines for beginners, solopreneurs, small businesses, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2008, Semrush describes itself as \"All-in-one digital marketing toolkit with powerful SEO and competitive analysis.\" Ubersuggest, established in 2017, positions itself as \"Neil Patel's affordable SEO tool for keyword ideas and site audits.\" With 9 years between them, Semrush brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Ubersuggest offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
19:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Semrush** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (9.0 vs 6.0), more features (10 vs 9). However, this does not mean Ubersuggest is a poor choice — far from it. Ubersuggest excels in its own right, particularly for beginners and solopreneurs.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value most comprehensive seo toolkit available, go with Semrush. If very affordable with lifetime plan option matters more to you, Ubersuggest is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
